Reasoning: 
1. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with text mining and finding related Stack Overflow posts, which falls under the domain of information retrieval. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper deals with natural language processing and text mining, which falls under the domain of computation and language. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of machine learning methods, including deep learning and SVM, and proposes a faster method for text classification. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with the use of AI methods, including deep learning and SVM, for text classification. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods in software engineering and proposes a faster method for text classification, which falls under the domain of software engineering.
